title: Dixie Cafe
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, American, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. This is an American diner with a Norman Rockwell atmosphere. They offer some vegan choices, but more vegetarian. Their vegetable heaven platter is consisted of your choosing from their large selection of sides. They offer vegetable kids' meals. Management helpful. Note: Turnip greens contain meat.
